name: EtherPOAP
intro: Commemorating the most significant upgrade in Ethereum’s history
introduce: EtherPOAP is as series of community events created by the most ardent supporters and community members of the Ethereum ecosystem to issue a series of NFTs to commemorate the most historic Ethernet mergers. Dedicated to commemorating the Web3 premium ecosystem built on Ether, it was initiated by dozens of Web3 head organisations and produced, distributed, and incubated by the IPrinter DAO.
